  <Notes>
    <Note Caller="1" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References/>
      <Content>It is possible that παραιτέομαι[a] differs somewhat from αἰτέω, both in intensity as well as in focusing upon the source from which the grant is to be made.</Content>
    </Note>
    <Note Caller="2" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References/>
      <Content>There are probably certain differences of meaning in the terms in {D:34.41}, but without more distinctive contexts, it is difficult to determine the precise areas of meaning.</Content>
    </Note>
  </Notes>
